Module org.nasdanika.graph
Package org.nasdanika.graph.processor

Annotation Interface OutgoingEndpoint

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({FIELD,METHOD}) public @interface OutgoingEndpoint
Field or method to inject a matching outgoing endpoint. A method shall have one or two parameters. If a single parameter than the endpoint is passed to the method. If two parameters then the connection and endpoint are passed - it allows to use one method for more than one connection/endpoint.
Author:
Pavel
